videos.description: Gonzaga is out to an early lead against in-state rival Washington thanks to Josh Perkins throwing up the lob to Johnathan Williams for the huge alley-oop.
videos.headline: Gonzaga jumping early with huge alley-oop

videos.description: 1H (14:56) GONZ Jordan Mathews made Three Point Jumper. Assisted by Przemek Karnowski.
videos.headline: Jordan Mathews turns steal into potential 4 point play

videos.description: Gonzaga shows off how to run the fast break with Josh Perkins throwing the perfect bounce pass to Killian Tillie for the two-hand flush and-1.
videos.headline: Tillie finishes fast break with huge jam and-1

videos.description: 1H (11:40) GONZ Zach Collins made Dunk. Assisted by Josh Perkins.
videos.headline: Josh Perkins with the no look pass to Zach Collins who slams down the dunk
Markelle Fultz goes down with apparent leg injury
Zach Collins goes up for the aggressive block, but a foul is called

videos.description: Nigel Williams-Goss scores 23 points to help No. 8 Gonzaga to an easy 98-71 win over Washington.
videos.headline: Gonzaga cruises to victory over Washington
